  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK512">
<l>vāri perukki vaḷampaṭut tuṟṟavai</l>
<l>yārāyvāṉ ceyka viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let him do (the king's) work who can enlarge the sources (of revenue), increase wealth and considerately prevent the accidents (which would destroy it).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
